These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, country, folk, r&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lilac, grey, blood-red
House: ranch-style, townhouse, cape-cod, gothic-revival
City: liverpool, hamburg, prague, hannover
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard, snowmobile, train
 1. the fan of disco is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who likes blood-red is the person who likes blood-red##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
10. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
11. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
12. the cape-cod house is between the person who likes grey and the townhouse house##2
13. the fan of folk is the person driving the train##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of country##1
15. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the fan of country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre           | disco | folk | r&b  | country    |
| Color   | lilac     | blood-red   | grey  | red  |
| House           | townhouse        | cape-cod    | gothic-revival        | ranch-style |
| City         | hannover    | hamburg      | liverpool   | prague    |
| Transport     | quad-bike  | train     | skateboard | snowmobile |

