.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, juice, sprite
House: colonial, townhouse, gothic-revival, cape-cod
4 different games are played: domino, whist, chess, scrabble
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, analyst, entrepreneur, security-guard
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, lilac, aquamarine, azure
 1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 3. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 5. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
10. the colonial house is the person who likes azure##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
12. the manager is on the left of the person playing domino##1
13. the analyst is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice        | sprite       | cola    | fanta       |
| House         | gothic-revival | townhouse      | cape-cod | colonial |
| Game   | scrabble     | chess | whist  | domino   |
| Job   | analyst   | security-guard         | manager   | entrepreneur      |
| Color         | lilac      | white     | aquamarine    | azure      |

