.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy, marigold, amaryllis
City: san-francisco, prague, miami, paris
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, almond-milk, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, scientific, adventure
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, subway, train
 1. the person watching musical movies is the person drinking tea##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
10. the person who growsmarigold is the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
13. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsamaryllis##1
14. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Flower          | marigold | daisy | balloon-flower     | amaryllis |
| City           | miami  | paris   | san-francisco | prague  |
