.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
City: hamburg, paris, venice, new-york
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, go, canasta
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, fonseca, montecristo, oliveros
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, snake
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, january, august
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the montecristo-smoker is the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
 4. the oliveros-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 5. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
10. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
12. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing canasta##1
13. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
14. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
15. the person playing go is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| City         | new-york | paris    | hamburg | venice       |
| Game           | scrabble | backgammon  | canasta   | go |
