 8. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is the person watching action movies##1
12. the baccarat-smoker is the person watching documentary movies##1
13. the old-henry-smoker is in an even position##4
14. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
