 4. the fan of techno is the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is between the fan of salsa and the person traveling to venice##2
 7. the person drinking tea is between the cottage house and the ranch-style house##2
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
10. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person who growspoppy is the person traveling to venice##1
12. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

