11. the photographer is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
14. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage         | fanta | tea  | cola | sprite  |
| Food   | broccoli     | carrot    | pepper     | grapes      |
| Job   | project-manager  | photographer  | writer     | musician |
| Game           | domino      | whist | backgammon       | canasta     |
| Transport     | roller      | skateboard | quad-bike  | subway   |

