4 different games are played: go, poker, billiard, whist
 1. the person playing billiard is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the pakistani##1
 3. the person playing poker is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the analyst is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
 6. the colombian is on the right of the canadian##1
 7. the owner of the goat is the canadian##1
 8. the librarian is on the far left##1
 9. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
10. the analyst is on the left of the musician##1
11. the person playing go is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the goat##2
12. the analyst is the colombian##1
13. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's hobby is baking is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
